'''海馬的組成'''（hippocampal formation）為[[大腦|大腦]][[顳葉|內側顳葉]]的構造。有關該構造所包含的範圍，學界並沒有共識。有些學者認為海馬結構包含{{le|齒狀回|dentate gyrus}}、[[海马体|海马体]]和{{le|岬下腳|subiculum}}<ref name= Martin2003>{{cite book |last1= Martin|first1= JH|title= Neuroanatomy: text and atlas|edition= third|year= 2003|publisher= McGraw-Hill Companies|location= |isbn= 0-07-121237-X|page= 382|chapter= Lymbic system and cerebral circuits for emotions, learning, and memory|chapterurl= http://books.google.com.au/books?id=OUC4igr3O4sC&pg=PA382}}</ref>。有些則認為前岬下腳（presubiculum）、{{le|偏岬下腳|parasubiculum}}和[[内嗅皮层|内嗅皮层]]皆包含在內<ref name= Amaral2007-1a>{{cite book |last1= Amaral|first1= D|last2= Lavenex|first2= P|editor1-first= P|editor1-last= Anderson|editor2-first= R|editor2-last= Morris|editor3-first= D|editor3-last= Amaral|editor4-first= T|editor4-last= Bliss|editor5-last= I'Keefe|title= The hippocampus book|edition= first|year= 2007|publisher= Oxford University Press|location= New York|isbn=9780195100273 |page= 37|chapter= Hippocampal neuroanatomy|chapterurl= http://books.google.com.au/books?id=zg6oyF1DziQC&pg=PA37}}</ref>。海馬結構被認為對於人類的記憶、空間概念，和專注力上扮演重要的角色。而海马回的傳輸途徑在所有動物之間幾乎一樣<ref name= Amaral2007-1b>{{cite book |last1= Anderson|first1= P|last2= Morris|first2= R|last3= Amaral|first3= D|last4= Bliss|first4=T|last5=O'Keefe|first5=J|editor1-first= P|editor1-last= Anderson|editor2-first= R|editor2-last= Morris|editor3-first= D|editor3-last= Amaral|editor4-first= T|editor4-last= Bliss|editor5-last= I'Keefe|title= The hippocampus book|edition= first|year= 2007|publisher= Oxford University Press|location= New York|isbn= 9780195100273|page= 3|chapter= The hippocampal formation|chapterurl= http://books.google.com.au/books?id=zg6oyF1DziQC&pg=PA3|}}</ref>。



